---
title: Chicago-Style Italian Beef Sandwich with Parm Fries and Beef Dip
description: Chicago's best is on the menu tonight. This Windy City staple is a call and answer to a typical French Dip sandwich, but comes into its own with a mix of sautéed veg, cheese and a hearty broth. AND to round it all out, we've got some flavour-packed Parm fries on the side to sweeten the deal. This should help tide you over until you can get back to The Bean!
